# This is the Vercel project root (see .vercel/project.json) — Vercel has no
# "Root Directory" scoped subfolder to hide backend/ behind, so it must be
# excluded here instead. The Rust backend is hosted separately on Render
# (see render.yaml); Vercel never needs to see its source or build output.
